								<a target="_blank" href="/qw?s0=7&amp;s1=%e7%a9%86%e6%b3%b0">穆泰</a> 
								<a target="_blank" href="/qw?s0=7&amp;s1=%e5%a2%93%e5%bf%97%e9%93%ad">墓志铭</a> 
